   <description>Submits Detail View part, committing edits made to records in the Detail View.</description>
  
  <discussion>Submit the Detail View part to commit any edits that were made to the record shown in the Detail View. If you supply an optional argument of true, then the record is saved and a new record is shown. This allows you to do continuous data entry. </discussion>
 
 
 
 
